      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped sun-dried tomatoes </strong>with your <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock </strong>to the pot and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened</p>",
