      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy sun-dried tomato & spinach orzo</strong> and top with the <strong>pan-fried</strong> <strong>salmon</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted pine kernels</strong>, a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
